setGain

public void setGain(float gain)
Attempt to set the global gain (volume ish) for the play back. If the control is not supported this method has no effect. 1.0 will set maximum gain, 0.0 minimum gain

Parameters:
gain - The gain value

setBalance

public void setBalance(float balance)
Attempt to set the balance between the two speakers. -1.0 is full left speak, 1.0 if full right speaker. Anywhere in between moves between the two speakers. If the control is not supported this method has no effect

Parameters:
balance - The balance value
